:0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T05:44:30.000Z","msg":"試過去到先搵，要睏雜物房鋪床褥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30b16654dde3bca1532fd241b5e08c3e2db5c198","tid":911933,"uid":213665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6d702dc2a6ef207761a88ac34b57aa9bf36e908","tid":911933,"uid":63694,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T05:44:30.000Z","msg":"試過去到先搵，要睏雜物房鋪床褥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T06:30:15.000Z","msg":"咁幾錢先,有冇優惠"},{"pid":"a3cf3f623b6c9fb180132d2df954f9f78904d503","tid":911933,"uid":63694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30b16654dde3bca1532fd241b5e08c3e2db5c198","tid":911933,"uid":213665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6d702dc2a6ef207761a88ac34b57aa9bf36e908","tid":911933,"uid":63694,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T05:44:30.000Z","msg":"試過去到先搵，要睏雜物房鋪床褥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T06:30:15.000Z","msg":"咁幾錢先,有冇優惠"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T15:24:07.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n<br />\n試過兩次<br />\n<br />\n1<br />\n10年前係雅典，晚上9點幾。因為火車罷工而濟留，又無錢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n暑假旺季，揹住個袋行到斷腳都無位。行左好耐終於搵到間hostel肯收留我，係佢見我咁慘先比我睏。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n收10歐羅，正常床位半價，雜物房好多床單，比d床單圍住睏。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2<br />\n都係10多年前，大陸大西北d山卡拉地方旅行，果時邊有咁發達，邊有得book定。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有一樣野係以前唔係間間旅店可以接外賓。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n結果晚上8點去到個鎮仔，係一棟睇落會冧既旅館肯收我地，10蚊人仔，緊係狗衝<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原來個地下室好大，仲有10幾個人，一張張床褥放地下睏，好大陣味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過都頂硬上睏，奇就奇在張褥又幾好睏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第二朝旁邊唔同左人，我估係d司機睏幾粒鐘走果d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2889a6fedd0e91d1f06ee26cbad7af4c6f987ff","tid":911933,"uid":22426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T17:00:03.000Z","msg":"試過因為恐襲 即日轉機票去馬德里 <br />\n當日book一間hostel<br />\n呢間hostel係旅程中最平最好個間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"223b168d9736a3c8c3e75733dab6c005d5391592","tid":911933,"uid":138799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T19:23:37.000Z","msg":"試過當日朝早先book<br />\neg:0800 book 1200就去酒店攞房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實貴唔貴睇你住咩酒店同當時房供應（好似係咁）"}]}